      "content": "idk i just cant stop thinking about how nothing actually matters. like we're just these tiny specs on a rock and in a few billion years the sun is just gonna burn out and everything we ever did or felt will be gone. it feels so pointless to even try to keep going when the end is just... nothingness anyway.",
