      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's hard to see it as liberating though. it just feels heavy. like, if nothing matters and the end is certain, why are we forced to endure all the suffering and the struggle in the meantime? if there's no ultimate point, then why is the default just to keep suffering through it until we can't anymore? wouldn't it be more logical to just opt out early if there's nothing to gain?",
